{"tid":2395153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子趴車頭阻離去 肇禍女司機照掉頭逃逸再撼巴士","createTime":"2021-02-04T16:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T09:39:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9b74148fe8fe62b3d62f70fddd6fbe53cc4e02","tid":2395153,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kbPfOG9tE5FImjVdWw4cdQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/4cbf9320-66fb-11eb-95df-f8e5207ebd18\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FkbPfOG9tE5FImjVdWw4cdQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2F4cbf9320-66fb-11eb-95df-f8e5207ebd18&h=ab7c7180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗發生驚險交通事故！（睇片）現場元朗教育路36號對開，今晚(4日)8時37分，一輛私家車疑在上址撞及一輛停泊路邊的客貨車車尾，客貨車男司機報稱頭暈不適送院，私家車事後亦逃離現場。約10分鐘後，該私家車於距離現場約2公里外的元朗公路近十八鄉路迴旋處，撞及一輛269Ｍ路線九巴後翻側。據悉意外後，一名女子從車廂爬出，消防接報到場時已不見其蹤影，警方正調查事發起因，並追尋涉事司機下落。<br />\n<br />\n有途人於教育路目擊事發經過，並拍下影片及上傳至互聯網。有關片段顯示，起初私家車車頭緊貼客貨車車尾，私家車司機疑驅車後退離開，客貨車男司機擋在私家車前方阻止，惟女司機竟不作理會，驅車衝行撞向男子，使他趴在車頭擋風玻璃前，並大聲喝止。可惜，女司機依然繼續開車，私家車隨後越線掉頭離開，而男子仍趴在擋風玻璃前，片段到此結束，據悉他於約100米外被拋下。"},{"pid":"f895a959cc2713991264327c4472cdbcc1635ddb","tid":2395153,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"兩邊都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d7980af0e041a3eae2e93d2a49f1c2ada134dd","tid":2395153,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"女司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ddb2fcf140d35bc7164079f19ef7f881cd8252","tid":2395153,"uid":276440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"GTA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3853a6c259cebe350329628a317c579eb71bea43","tid":2395153,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:55:43.000Z","msg":"唔好撞啲咁出名既就得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d68469c2cf5e558057166022550f32e6de6d581","tid":2395153,"uid":80647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T09:08:52.000Z","msg":"女人真係唔可以揸車，咁同謀殺有咩分別"},{"pid":"add7d6186d5bb9b3ae2cdd3b84d1647606a9fd70","tid":2395153,"uid":134686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T09:12:30.000Z","msg":"班狗仲未拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140f5e32add91da0b12fa13d8baab30b35ca499c","tid":2395153,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"add7d6186d5bb9b3ae2cdd3b84d1647606a9fd70","tid":2395153,"uid":134686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T09:12:30.000Z","msg":"班狗仲未拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T09:17:44.000Z","msg":"果度係元朗呀, 班垃圾香港警察仲慢慢行緊, 私底下同條女傾緊點拆"},{"pid":"b8bef843032be9cd5bcf96bfcae913eaee8d7e3b","tid":2395153,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T09:39:25.000Z","msg":"另外，有網民再上載一條片段，見涉事私家車女司機撞車後，手持數個外賣飯盒站在車旁，並致電向親友求助，指客貨車司機初時要求賠償1000港元，其後再加至2000港元，女司機要求對方翻查附近店舖「天眼」，惟客貨車司機指其說謊。其後，女司機向電話中親友指出：「佢（客貨車司機）都唔知自己架車畀人撞咗！」<br />\n此外，有網民指女司機在意外前，在附近的食肆水門雞飯買外賣，水門雞飯其後在社交網站分享片段，並留言指「Staff話佢入嚟嘅時候已經跳跳地」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫你補返2段"}]}